ol        Code공개가 보안과 직결되는 것은 아니다         내부적인 복잡한 설정파일들과 코드를 분리하는 작업을 잘 하면 코드를 그대로 가져와도 재현이 불가능하게 하면 된다     스터디가 필요함            발표자의 회사에선 Terraform & Packer & Ansible 구현을 하는 Workflow를 구축        VPC구성을 어떻게 할까?         reInvent 자료를 토대로 참조하는 게 제일 좋다     발표자 회사에선 VPC peering 을 활용하고 있다고 함            Subnetting         public / private로 잡는다            배포를 코드화 해서 버저닝을 한다        AWS의 Cloudformation대신에 Terraform이 더 간단하며, AWS에서 공식적으로 인정하고 있다고 함        Immutable Infrastructure         container                 Netflix는 어떻게 쓰고 있는가         Golden Image만들어서 관리            Aws slow start ?        Auto scaling의 기준?         Cpu만을 지표로 해야하나?     요청수를 기준으로도 할 수 있다            DevSecOps ??         Sec는 security     Security as code     Checklist를 문서로 작성하지 말고 코드 안으로 녹여라. Vulnerability, test, ...            보안기능이 탑재된 무료 메신저&sns         Keybase.io     바이너리 파일도 암호화 가능            측정하라 Measurement         IT performance            Deplyment frequency      Lead time      Mean time to recover      Change failure rate               Unpplanned work                 Change management        Disaster Recovery Management        Chaos Engineering         외국에선 현재진행형     Failure as a service     Form을 만들어서 보고서로 정리            Sharing         이슈 발생하면 모두에게 공유되게 함     서비스가 몇년이 지나면 처음부터 다시 만들기     개개인마다 결정권한을 갖게 한다     기술을 바꾸는것보다 마인드셋 바꾸는게 다 어렵다     한 가지로 다 해결되는 것은 더이상 없다..                                      ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:12px;top:168px;width:576px\">\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">Serverless<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBAA8;&#xC784;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBC1C;&#xD45C;&#xC790; : &#xC1A1;&#xC8FC;&#xC601; &#xC0BC;&#xC131;&#xC804;&#xC790;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">AOL?</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Communication layer &#xC81C;&#xAC70; ?</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Agile is changing thinking</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">DevOps is changing doing</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Datadog : monitoring tool</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Code&#xACF5;&#xAC1C;&#xAC00; &#xBCF4;&#xC548;&#xACFC; &#xC9C1;&#xACB0;&#xB418;&#xB294; &#xAC83;&#xC740; &#xC544;&#xB2C8;&#xB2E4;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB0B4;&#xBD80;&#xC801;&#xC778; &#xBCF5;&#xC7A1;&#xD55C; &#xC124;&#xC815;&#xD30C;&#xC77C;&#xB4E4;&#xACFC; &#xCF54;&#xB4DC;&#xB97C; &#xBD84;&#xB9AC;&#xD558;&#xB294; &#xC791;&#xC5C5;&#xC744; &#xC798; &#xD558;&#xBA74; &#xCF54;&#xB4DC;&#xB97C; &#xADF8;&#xB300;&#xB85C; &#xAC00;&#xC838;&#xC640;&#xB3C4; &#xC7AC;&#xD604;&#xC774; &#xBD88;&#xAC00;&#xB2A5;&#xD558;&#xAC8C; &#xD558;&#xBA74; &#xB41C;&#xB2E4;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC2A4;&#xD130;&#xB514;&#xAC00; &#xD544;&#xC694;&#xD568;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBC1C;&#xD45C;&#xC790;&#xC758; &#xD68C;&#xC0AC;&#xC5D0;&#xC120; Terraform &amp; Packer &amp; Ansible &#xAD6C;&#xD604;&#xC744; &#xD558;&#xB294; Workflow&#xB97C; &#xAD6C;&#xCD95;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">VPC&#xAD6C;&#xC131;&#xC744; &#xC5B4;&#xB5BB;&#xAC8C; &#xD560;&#xAE4C;?</span></p>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">reInvent &#xC790;&#xB8CC;&#xB97C; &#xD1A0;&#xB300;&#xB85C; &#xCC38;&#xC870;&#xD558;&#xB294; &#xAC8C; &#xC81C;&#xC77C; &#xC88B;&#xB2E4;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBC1C;&#xD45C;&#xC790; &#xD68C;&#xC0AC;&#xC5D0;&#xC120; VPC peering &#xC744; &#xD65C;&#xC6A9;&#xD558;&#xACE0; &#xC788;&#xB2E4;&#xACE0; &#xD568;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">Subnetting</span></p>\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span lang><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">public / private&#xB85C; &#xC7A1;&#xB294;&#xB2E4;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xBC30;&#xD3EC;&#xB97C; &#xCF54;&#xB4DC;&#xD654; &#xD574;&#xC11C; &#xBC84;&#xC800;&#xB2DD;&#xC744; &#xD55C;&#xB2E4;</span></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<p lang style=\"font-family:Calibri;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">AWS<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC758;</span> Cloudformation<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB300;&#xC2E0;&#xC5D0;</span> Terraform<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC774;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB354;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC04;&#xB2E8;&#xD558;&#xBA70;</span>, AWS<span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC5D0;&#xC11C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xACF5;&#xC2DD;&#xC801;&#xC73C;&#xB85C;</span> <span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC778;&#xC815;&#xD5